g: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">学生时代赴日留学后，黄峰丽在日本工作生活了十余年。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">也许是生来对“美”就有执念，她将工作之余的所有闲暇，都投资到“生活美学”这件事上。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">她学习摄影，经久打磨，成为了独立摄影师。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">她系统性地学习了餐桌设计、花艺设计、收纳整理、室内设计，每学一样，都将其滋养成了自己的生存和生活技能。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 546px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px; border-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(211, 206, 206); border-right-color: rgb(211, 206, 206); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">“我在日本一开始学的是摄影，就单纯想要拍出美美的照片。学的过程中发现，摄影和对生活的感悟之间有很大的联系，除了光影技术之外，其实更多的是摄影者对拍摄事物的领悟程度。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">你想拍出什么样的美好生活，得先自己过上那样美的生活。”</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 2px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 273px; border-style: none; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(255, 211, 196); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 269px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px -2.5em; padding: 0px; width: 2.5em; height: 2.5em; border-left: 2px dotted rgba(255, 196, 196, 0.76); border-top: 2px dotted rgba(255, 196, 196, 0.76); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px; box-sizing: border