<section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 529.609px; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 0px; display: inline-block; width: 529.609px; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/22272400_1537516720.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngwej1zicqpzzal5php7d7yet4zpqhy5zdgjvpkpdibyk3ia45e9zh9wscnquupla0j7rwsiadahepnpq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(133, 121, 126); letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;">因为她，我开始坚信，这世间真有这样一种能力，是不论抽到怎样糟糕的“烂牌”，都能打出一副好人生。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box;">文|小麦（课程开发师）</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px -16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/33035900_1537516720.cn/mmbiz_png/2j0wag3eiaydnsuhjbnxcrtfkuzbiccvsolsyhepe2zyg9r6awpednoj8ibw8yjkhlsiand9o4aohqwsc9pkn6m3eq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">两个月前，我参加了一位生活美学老师的线下课程。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">上课第一天，她就收到了全体学员的“膝盖”。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">课程安排是在工作日的上海。大家纷纷从各处赶来，面带倦色，风尘仆仆。</p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">开始上课前，我们收到了一位同期学员的退学消息。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">原因是，高峰时段他上不了高架，堵了一个小时没挪动，心浮气躁、心灰意冷之际，选择放弃这次课程。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">我们听说后都很惋惜，一顿数落大城市拥挤的交通，这一话题也顺势成为学员们的破冰开场白，大家倾诉着赶来上课的辛劳。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">其中一位同学不经意感慨：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">“咱们要比惨，那估计没人惨得过老师了吧？她昨晚估计睡了4小时不到。”</span><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">原来，老师前一天从大连乘机飞上海，不想海上大雾，航班延误停飞。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为了不耽误上课，她临时辗转到沈阳机场，又经历了漫长的延误后，凌晨三点抵达上海。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">能想象的出，遇到这样不顺心的航程，候机楼积攒的怨气，估计都能冲破房顶。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">老师对此毫无抱怨，还言笑平时太懒一个月只能看一本书，有幸可以在那样封闭式的等待中，一口气读完了5本书。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">有一句禅语，智者转心不转境。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">那位退掉课程的同学，因心情变差而选择放弃，正是我常见的大多数人的做法。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">老师则透出“转心不转境”的智慧。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/43025100_1537516720.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngwej1zicqpzzal5php7d7yehmzmg7r90b5vwgicboh5jgxjqscgsoqxiatarbxhka0m4zb9pqexv6uq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section sty