<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/82890600_1537516723.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshniakzjgcqscsfibmibevfurvykblyqr4buvouplhq7mqvxuqdk5e6ibov8jahf43oicmbwxib1zuqgbgla/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: -2.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 2.5em; height: 2.5em; float: right; border-right: 2px dotted rgba(255, 196, 196, 0.76); border-bottom: 2px dotted rgba(255, 196, 196, 0.76); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">当下的时代，人们潜意识里依旧把“忙”奉为神圣的生产力，依旧认为“闲暇”是奢侈和罪恶，歌颂着“苦行僧”式的幸福获取路径。</span></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">蒋勋在《生活十讲》中有提到一个观点：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(241, 175, 175); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(241, 175, 175); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">“物化”也许是“忙”的背后，更深层的空虚。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">不论是“忙”，还是物质追求，不过是渡人去“好好生活”的船，一旦把船当成了彼岸，忘记了这一切努力不过是要让生活更幸福的目的，那生活回报你的，只有似汪洋般一望无际的虚无。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">我很喜欢峰丽姐对“好好生活”的“好”字，写过的一句随笔：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(241, 175, 175); box-sizing: border-box;">“好”字多么奢侈，要读书明心智，要旅行展视界，要劳作砺手足，要时间让一切醇熟，酵化沉淀至拥有丰富的简单和平静。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(31, 73, 121); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;">▼▼&nbsp;&nbsp;黄峰丽人生整理课预告片▼&nbsp;▼&nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><iframe class="video_iframe wx_video_iframe" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" width="558" height="314" src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/video_tmpl&vid=w0704zxexl9"></iframe><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-color: rgb(249, 174, 165); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: -10px 0px; padding: 0px 10px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 546px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; border-width: 2px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); background-color: rgba(246, 212, 218, 0.58); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(110, 110, 110); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">人生整理清单 | 音频课——</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;">全面提升“幸福力”，过上有序、有效且美的生活</p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 20px; height: 20px; float: right; background-color: rgb(249, 174, 165); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/92376000_1537516723.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngwej1zicqpzzal5php7d7ye435cfn6ib2nu8lnjowmfwxmbk8koetrvwowwiaukh1ia20bibf2oiye6xq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">Q：学习这套课程，最大的收获将会是什么？</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">峰丽：</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">清除获得美好人生路上不必要的负累，掌控自己的行为、深度探索自己独特的美好人生，提升感知幸福的能力。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">三个方面，也对应了我提出的：过上有序、有效且美的生活。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">想要帮助大家不但获得当下的幸福，也能在这样日复一日的训练中最终掌控人生，达到长远的人生理想。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: -4px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 546px; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 50px; height: 4px; background-color: rgb(125, 106, 96); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">Q：课程设计中，觉得哪里最用心？</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">峰丽：</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">清单吧。配合每节课帮助大家解决的问题，我整理了出了16套清单。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">清单有点像帮助大家在日常中，不断自我训练的工具，可以帮助大家，梳理和落实思维的整理。<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">整个课程其实是我自己知识和经验的总结，我自己也在用这些方法，去解决我面对的问题。我自己也是在不断进行自我修正和提升的路上。</p></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: -4px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 546px; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 50px; height: 4px; background-color: rgb(125, 106, 96); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/1968200_1537516724.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngwej1zicqpzzal5php7d7yekoics9rwspzly4jawksgxqacz54htr5yoczouibte2navhwreibgtgyoq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px; display: inline-block; width: 464.094px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(250, 209, 209); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 176.516px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; transform: translate3d(-20px, 0px, 0px); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.1em 0.3em; display: inline-block; border-width: 2px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 235, 235); background-color: rgb(238, 235, 235); color: rgb(235, 152, 152); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">课程亮点</strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 285.562px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: right; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">•&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">从活出“日常幸福力”角度出发，整合管理学、心灵成长、生活美学多领域精髓要义，快速习得掌控人生的智慧</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">•&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">每课节提供方法实践工具——人生整理清单，辅助“意识”到“行为”的落实</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">•&nbsp;升级“生活整理”至“人生整理”，深度剖析生活失控的本质，梳理自我专属的幸福地图，提升感受幸福、创造幸福的能力</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px; display: inline-block; width: 464.094px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(250, 209, 209); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">•本课程为音频课程，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">课程订阅后不支持退款。</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>

「第十一课」以手抵心，进行“物”的美学升级 —— 生活美学入门（下集）

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app2lcEpf8H5681/a_5bd9856e76a86_hhK3KLM3

<section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 529.609px; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 0px; display: inline-block; width: 529.609px; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/22272400_1537516720.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngwej1zicqpzzal5php7d7yet4zpqhy5zdgjvpkpdibyk3ia45e9zh9wscnquupla0j7rwsiadahepnpq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(133, 121, 126); letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;">因为她，我开始坚信，这世间真有这样一种能力，是不论抽到怎样糟糕的“烂牌”，都能打出一副好人生。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box;">文|小麦（课程开发师）</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px -16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/33035900_1537516720.cn/mmbiz_png/2j0wag3eiaydnsuhjbnxcrtfkuzbiccvsolsyhepe2zyg9r6awpednoj8ibw8yjkhlsiand9o4aohqwsc9pkn6m3eq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">两个月前，我参加了一位生活美学老师的线下课程。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">上课第一天，她就收到了全体学员的“膝盖”。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">课程安排是在工作日的上海。大家纷纷从各处赶来，面带倦色，风尘仆仆。</p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">开始上课前，我们收到了一位同期学员的退学消息。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">原因是，高峰时段他上不了高架，堵了一个小时没挪动，心浮气躁、心灰意冷之际，选择放弃这次课程。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">我们听说后都很惋惜，一顿数落大城市拥挤的交通，这一话题也顺势成为学员们的破冰开场白，大家倾诉着赶来上课的辛劳。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">其中一位同学不经意感慨：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">“咱们要比惨，那估计没人惨得过老师了吧？她昨晚估计睡了4小时不到。”</span><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">原来，老师前一天从大连乘机飞上海，不想海上大雾，航班延误停飞。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为了不耽误上课，她临时辗转到沈阳机场，又经历了漫长的延误后，凌晨三点抵达上海。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">能想象的出，遇到这样不顺心的航程，候机楼积攒的怨气，估计都能冲破房顶。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">老师对此毫无抱怨，还言笑平时太懒一个月只能看一本书，有幸可以在那样封闭式的等待中，一口气读完了5本书。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">有一句禅语，智者转心不转境。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">那位退掉课程的同学，因心情变差而选择放弃，正是我常见的大多数人的做法。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">老师则透出“转心不转境”的智慧。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/43025100_1537516720.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngwej1zicqpzzal5php7d7yehmzmg7r90b5vwgicboh5jgxjqscgsoqxiatarbxhka0m4zb9pqexv6uq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; font-size: 11px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); line-height: 1.8; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;">▲<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">本文中所用图片，均来自黄峰丽</span></span></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">课上完时，我竟有种对生活“开悟”的感觉！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我开始坚信，这世间真有这样一种能力，是不论抽到怎样糟糕的“烂牌”，都能打出一副好人生。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">这位生活美学家，叫黄峰丽。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">她就是传说中那种，“把日子过成诗”、“过上了90%的姑娘梦中生活”的人。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">她本真的生活状态，“美到让人没有抵抗力”。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 36px; transform: translate3d(20px, 0px, 0px); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: auto; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 3em; height: 3em; vertical-align: top; background-position: 34.0909% 33.5069%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 127.668%; display: i