 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">6年前，因为家庭原因，黄峰丽回到国内，开始了自由职业的生活模式。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 546px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px; border-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(211, 206, 206); border-right-color: rgb(211, 206, 206); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">“以前总觉得自己的价值，就是给公司带来的价值，现在的生活让我感受到，生活本身的意义就存在于每一天的快乐里。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">美好事物的诱惑源源不断，工作也是生活，这是距离我自己更近的状态。”</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">黄峰丽记录自己的生活，打动、诱惑着越来越多的人。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">2015年，她开设了自己的生活美学空间—工<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">倉</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">，生活美学课程，也在那之后，逐渐丰富起来。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">一波又一波生活美学的爱好者，千里迢迢，来赴一场美的盛宴。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 273px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/12851900_1537516722.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshniakzjgcqscsfibmibevfurvykibyu39figyezp0tcphjttioyu4pobppx7fvbetlqqaibdppmgjbzevgw/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-bo