argin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 50px; height: 4px; background-color: rgb(125, 106, 96); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(130, 100, 74); line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">Q：课程设计中，觉得哪里最用心？</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">峰丽：</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">清单吧。配合每节课帮助大家解决的问题，我整理了出了16套清单。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">清单有点像帮助大家在日常中，不断自我训练的工具，可以帮助大家，梳理和落实思维的整理。<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">整个课程其实是我自己知识和经验的总结，我自己也在用这些方法，去解决我面对的问题。我自己也是在不断进行自我修正和提升的路上。</p></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: -4px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; width: 546px; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 50px; height: 4px; background-color: rgb(125, 106, 96); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/1968200_1537516724.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngwej1zicqpzzal5php7d7yekoics9rwspzly4jawksgxqacz54htr5yoczouibte2navhwreibgtgyoq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px; display: inline-block; width: 464.094px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(250, 209, 209); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; 