p;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">每课节提供方法实践工具——人生整理清单，辅助“意识”到“行为”的落实</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">•&nbsp;升级“生活整理”至“人生整理”，深度剖析生活失控的本质，梳理自我专属的幸福地图，提升感受幸福、创造幸福的能力</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px; display: inline-block; width: 464.094px; vertical-align: top; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(250, 209, 209); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">•本课程为音频课程，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">课程订阅后不支持退款。</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>

「第十一课」以手抵心，进行“物”的美学升级 —— 生活美学入门（上集）

