</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;">全面提升“幸福力”，过上有序、有效且美的生活</p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 20px; height: 20px; float: right; background-color: rgb(249, 174, 165); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/92376000_1537516723.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngwej1zicqpzzal5php7d7ye435cfn6ib2nu8lnjowmfwxmbk8koetrvwowwiaukh1ia20bibf2oiye6xq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-