 0px; padding: 0px; width: 546px; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important; max-height: 1.2em !important;"/>&nbsp;<section style="margin: -0.9em auto 0.9em; padding: 0px; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 1px; padding: 0px; width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(235, 152, 152); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">去年初秋，我去拜访她，想请她做一套虚度的线上美学课程。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">几天朝夕相处，听她身边相熟的人说，黄峰丽待生活，有种“魔力”：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(241, 175, 175); box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(241, 175, 175); box-sizing: border-box;">不仅能让岁月予她多点照拂，谁在她身边待久了，自己的日子都能变得“美”起来。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">这魔力，我信！</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">即便我忘记了那一日具体聊了什么，但她带给我的“明媚”，却在记忆里撒了种子，时隔四季竟生了根，念念不忘。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">那之后，她的课程，陆续开发打磨了7个月之久。这一年的相处，终于让我“参透”了她的“魔力”：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(241, 175, 175); box-sizing: border-box;">那是一种幸福力！一种正向的能量，一种感知幸福、并创造幸福的能力。</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(241, 175, 175); box-sizing: border-box;">我们初见时的那一束“明媚”，就是我久违的幸福感。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">“幸福力”这个词，的确熟悉又生僻，毕竟书本与职场，都没有教授过这种由“好好生活”产生的能力。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">好好生活，很多时候是被我们主动选择忽略的，因为害怕失去，失去“忙”。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app3T7ATDSc1195/image/ueditor/28471000_1537516723.cn/mmbiz_jpg/uliackyshngwej1zicqpzzal5php7d7yeib2oxqicvkpp8lmjov3jvfqfm3jqmue3f4akh5cthlxniclcdvict0o63w/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 2px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 273px; border-style: none; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(255, 211, 196); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 269px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px -2.5em; padding: 0px; width: 2